{
 "name": "RPlog_Mission_to_Forlec",
 "title": "Mission to Forlec",
 "summary": "On the canyon world of Forlec, Admiral Danik Kreldin commands a small temporary Imperial outpost gathering intelligence for a planned invasion of Caspar, defended by two platoons of stormtroopers and assault bombers. When sensors flag an incoming New Republic vessel, Kreldin scrambles his fighters and rouses his troops. Aboard the inbound transport, Colonel Sabrina Rheatis leads a hand-picked SpecOps team of marines, including the veteran Sergeant Stoneface, preparing for a combat drop onto the contested outpost. The log sets the stage for the clash between Kreldin's Imperials and Rheatis's New Republic strike force over the recon base.",
